Bartolo’s Cigars & Wine
Bartolo’s Cafe
104 NE 2nd Ave Suite 100
Delray Beach, FL 33444
(561) 562-6996
Contact
Privacy Policy

Bartolo’s Cigars & Wine is the perfect destination for lovers of the finer things in life, from cigars, to wine, to artisanal coffee and chocolate. Our cigars are curated from a wide selection of high-end, premium handmade cigars by the owners who have over two decades of experience in the cigar industry. Our exclusive boutique wines have also been carefully selected from some of the best wineries in France, California, Spain, Chile, Argentina, and more.
Inside our store, Bartolo's Cafe offers a variety of exquisite baked goods and locally-crafted artisanal chocolates, as well as a menu that can be enjoyed while sitting at the bar or at a table with a glass of wine or beer. Bartolo's also offers smoothies, teas, and gourmet coffees, iced or hot to enhance your experience in beautiful Delray Beach.
While our venue is non-smoking, those that would like to enjoy a cigar are welcome to sit outside at one of our tables.
